45
00:05:22.937 --> 00:05:24.471
Bună, mamă.

46
00:05:24.504 --> 00:05:26.774
Da, lucrurile merg foarte bine.

47
00:05:26.808 --> 00:05:27.808
Eu doar...

48
00:05:30.945 --> 00:05:32.780
Tocmai am

49
